Halisahar is famous for Ramprasad Sen, the saint,the great 'Kali' devotee, creator of 'Ramprasadi songs'. One can find many ashrams here, the famous Nigamananda Asram is at Halisahar. Sri Chaitannya Mahaprabhu's Guru Griha is situated near 'Chaitannya Doba'. Both Rani Rashmoni and Sadhak Ramprasad Sen were born here. There is a tourist spot - the "Ramprasad Vita" which was the cottage of Sadhak Ramprasad was born. Halisahar is also known as a birthland of freedom fighter Bipin Bihari Ganguly.Malancha railway level crossing.
